  "name": "Restart service from Datadog alert and send to PagerDuty",
  "description": "n8n workflow template from ritik-prog/n8n-automation-templates-5000: Restart service from Datadog alert and send to PagerDuty",
  "category": "Data",
  "tags": [
    "n8n 2000 workflows",
